Add Podman container engine support

Add a containerEngine preference for local execution and image builds.
Auto resolves Docker first and Podman as a fallback. Support local
Podman execution and Podman build/push for Kubernetes configurations
without a Docker buildx builder.

Document the interface and add a Podman test harness mode for
devcontainer smoke tests.

Add default Podman smoke coverage and expose `cargo xtest --executor
podman` as the full-suite Podman redirect. The Podman test harness can
run inside restricted devcontainers through Podman's rootful service.
